headline: Kenvue Stock Has Unusual Put Option Activity After Lower Q2 Sales and CEO Firing
summary: Kenvue, which manufactures Band-Aid, Listerine, Neutrogena, and Johnson's consumer products, reported disappointing Q2 sales and just announced that its CEO had left. Put options are showing unusually high volume today.
